    <pre>The results box that appears on the /people/ page needs a UI re-design. This is an open-ended UI 
design assignment. 

If you're interested in doing a re-design of the /people/ page, please assign yourself this ticket and 
attach mockup(s) . Fee free to ping any Open Hatch people on IRC to get the discussion going.</pre>
